{"type": "article", "id": 5542, "title": "Airy 系列灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-26T07:19:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234001WltTSqm8RgHYyJz6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自日本的设计公司 24° Studio 最近带来了一系列新作 Airy，选择日本米纸为主要原料进行制造。表面的迭片纹理可以有效阻止材料锈蚀和撕裂。米纸的特质使得这一系列灯具能够带来一种柔和的漫射照明效果，当灯具打开时，其独特的几何结构也为空间带来了别致的照明体验。Airy 系列提供吊灯与落地灯两种款型 4 个尺寸的选择。定价 115－225 欧元（约合人民币 803－1572 元）不等，<a href=\"http://store.24d-studio.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233958YFI16nBTQD4khqLt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523395969PhYiFul8oEk1vc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.778125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233959vnskuGTx8mbHIoAN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66891892\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234000xINyse0LqUbu3Jo6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}